show_name: Cardfight!! Vanguard: High School Arc Cont. (TV)
other_title: カードファイト！！ ヴァンガード 続・高校生編 (Japanese)
plot: Aichi Sendou and the Miyaji Cardfight Club aim the win the national championship, but problems arise after the timeline has been rewritten and taken Kourin off the team. Now Aichi and company must find a way to get back to 5 members to compete while the Student Council tries to shut them down. Meanwhile Kai battles his own demons as he tries to figure out how to reconnect with his cards, and Kouji Ibuki must decide whether he wants to give up the game or find a new way to play that doesn't involve deleting others.
